      <div id="description" slot="content" class="style-scope ytd-video-secondary-info-renderer"><yt-formatted-string class="content style-scope ytd-video-secondary-info-renderer" force-default-style="" split-lines="">How to Setup GitHub Pages in 2018 and create a Data Science Portfolio.

Check out our website for Data Science tips in 2018:
<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/redirect?redir_token=xztPao0LFqiWbqJ3AIw5kUK6rdF8MTU2OTc3NzAwMEAxNTY5NjkwNjAw&amp;v=qWrcgHwSG8M&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dataoptimal.com&amp;event=video_description" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">https://www.dataoptimal.com</a>

Subscribe for even more Data Science tutorials! 
<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/redirect?redir_token=xztPao0LFqiWbqJ3AIw5kUK6rdF8MTU2OTc3NzAwMEAxNTY5NjkwNjAw&amp;v=qWrcgHwSG8M&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2J2O5N8&amp;event=video_description" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">https://bit.ly/2J2O5N8</a>

Follow us on Twitter!
<a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/redirect?redir_token=xztPao0LFqiWbqJ3AIw5kUK6rdF8MTU2OTc3NzAwMEAxNTY5NjkwNjAw&amp;v=qWrcgHwSG8M&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDataOptimal&amp;event=video_description" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">https://twitter.com/DataOptimal</a>

Link to the code used in this video: <a class="yt-simple-endpoint style-scope yt-formatted-string" spellcheck="false" href="https://www.youtube.com/redirect?redir_token=xztPao0LFqiWbqJ3AIw5kUK6rdF8MTU2OTc3NzAwMEAxNTY5NjkwNjAw&amp;v=qWrcgHwSG8M&amp;q=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fdataoptimal%2Fgithub-pages-tutorial&amp;event=video_description" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">https://github.com/dataoptimal/github...</a>

In this tutorial I'm going to help you set up a beautiful data science portfolio using GitHub pages and Jekyll.  

I'll show you step-by-step how to create a data science portfolio.

Together we'll create an amazing looking data science project page, home page, and about page.  

I'll also show you how to create links from your data science portfolio homepage to your GitHub, and linked profiles.  This will help your projects gain exposure with potential employers.
